oc:kn_66247323 a oc:AntiPattern,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When performing lead qualification" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Do not qualify too quickly or ignore red flags. Avoid assuming budget equals ability to buy, and never forget to re-qualify over time as situations change." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Premature qualification wastes sales resources on low-probability deals; missed red flags lead to stalled pipelines." ;
    oc:severityLevel "HIGH" .

oc:kn_70b6be79 a oc:Constraint,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "Always — inherent limitations of this skill" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Cannot access CRM data directly, scoring requires defined criteria from the user, cannot verify provided information externally, and human judgment is still essential for final decisions." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Setting proper expectations prevents over-reliance on automated scoring without human validation." ;
    oc:severityLevel "MEDIUM" .

oc:kn_79745d60 a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:Standard ;
    oc:appliesToContext "During any lead qualification process" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Ask open-ended questions to get context, verify information directly rather than assuming, document everything in CRM, re-qualify regularly, and know when to walk away." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Consistent qualification discipline improves close rates and prevents pipeline pollution with unqualified deals." ;
    oc:severityLevel "MEDIUM" .

oc:kn_a78bdaf4 a oc:DesignPrinciple,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When building a lead scoring model" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Use a composite scoring approach combining Fit Score (demographics: company and contact) and Engagement Score (behavioral: website, email, events) alongside a qualification framework (BANT, MEDDIC, or GPCTBA/C&I)." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Multi-dimensional scoring captures both who the lead is and how they behave, yielding more accurate qualification." ;
    oc:severityLevel "MEDIUM" .

oc:kn_e7207c6a a oc:Heuristic,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "Before beginning detailed lead evaluation" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Always run the Disqualification Criteria Check (company size, geography, budget authority, timeline, competitor lock-in) before investing effort in full qualification." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Early disqualification saves significant time by filtering out leads that will never convert." ;
    oc:severityLevel "HIGH" .

